			<div class="content" id="post-content-2321846">
									

<p>So I got inspired and wrote a short thing about Doctor Bright and SCP 348. I showed it to some off-site folks and they liked it more than I thought they would. So I wrote another thing about 166 and 348. And they liked that too.<br />
So I wrote a third thing with the Black Queen and 348, and then put them all together on my sandbox, and brought them to chat. Got some feedback, tweaked 'em up, but then never posted them.<br />
But since it's an appropriate day, and I think they're about as good as they're going to get, here they all are.<br />
I hope everyone has/is having/had a happy Father's Day. Whether it's with your dad or not.</p>

