				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dewman" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(628488); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=628488&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610251309" alt="Dewman" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=628488)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dewman" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(628488); return false;" >Dewman</a></span> <span class="odate time_1435038281 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">23 Jun 2015 05:44</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2322902">
									

<p>Maybe? I did my best to write each segment so that they could be enjoyed without knowing the history behind them, with the name reveal being a kind of transition from where she goes from The Black Queen Who Is So Crafty And Clever to Alison Who Just Wants To Know If Dad Still Even Remembers Her. I don't know if that counts as her name meaning something, but that was what I was trying to do while writing it. The name wasn't what meant anything, except that she stopped being The Black Queen in that moment.</p>

							</div>

								
					
