			<div class="content" id="post-content-2324367">
									

<p>Well, the shift from Black Queen to &quot;just a human person&quot; worked. Honestly, that could have been accomplished simply by calling her &quot;Alison&quot; and not &quot;The Black Queen&quot; anymore. It was really the reveal of her last name that made me wonder if I should know it, of it had any links to anything else on the site.</p>

