														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2325212">
									

<p>Yeah, I can see what you mean. Mostly it was just because I knew (what is commonly headcanon'd as) her full name, so I decided to just roll with that. I got it from other Black Queen tales, but it's not mean to be a connector, so much a so little detail meant as a &quot;oh okay so that's her real name&quot; for someone who doesn't know the reference, and a &quot;ohh I get it&quot; for people who do.</p>

